{"ProductId":"26","Title":"Canyon Ridge<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Modern","ShortDescription":"Faux wood insulated garage doors with contemporary style","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/canyon-ridge-modern-roulette-medium-clear-cypress-showcase.webp?sfvrsn=890cb293_1","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/canyon-ridge-modern-garage-doors","Overview":"<h3>Built for Modern Living</h3><h4>Engineered Strength</h4><p>Every Canyon Ridge&reg; Modern garage door has four layers &mdash; steel, insulation, more steel, and a tough faux-wood cladding with fiberglass-filled boards &mdash; all working together to deliver increased durability and security. Aesthetically, the doors have been updated with chamfered horizontal edges to create a refreshed, modern look.</p><h4>Faux Wood, Real Texture</h4><p>The composite cladding and overlays are molded from genuine wood pieces, so you get the rich texture and natural grain of Clear Cypress or Mahogany, without the maintenance headaches real wood brings. Choose from a range of paint and stain options to suit your home&rsquo;s style.</p><h4>Design Your Door</h4><p>With eight distinct door designs, optional slim windows or metal accents, and a palette of eight standard finishes (plus more than 1,500 <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/colorblast\">Color Blast&reg; custom colors</a>), it&rsquo;s easy to create a look that&rsquo;s truly yours.</p><h4>Superior Insulation</h4><p>Each door is packed with 2\" <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a>, keeping your garage comfortable and energy efficient. R-values range from 6.3 to 20.4, depending on your chosen design.</p><h4>Weather Ready</h4><p>For homes in high-wind regions, <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/wind\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement</a> is available for added peace of mind.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Canyon Ridge&reg; Modern Construction</h3><p>The Canyon Ridge&reg; Modern garage door is engineered for lasting performance, comfort, and peace of mind. At its core is a tough steel base, built to withstand daily use and provide a solid foundation for your door. On top of this, you&rsquo;ll find low-maintenance, moisture-resistant composite overlays that capture the warmth and look of real wood, but won&rsquo;t rot, warp, or crack &mdash; even with heavy exposure to the elements.</p><img src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/cutaway-canyon-ridge-modern.webp?sfvrsn=8afd9d92_3\" alt=\"Canyon Ridge Modern\" sf-size=\"100\" /><ol><li>Cladding or Overlay (Full-View)</li><li>Steel</li><li>2\" Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol><p>Inside, each door is filled with 2\" of Clopay&rsquo;s proprietary <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a>. This advanced foam technology fills every inch of the door, making it warmer, quieter, and stronger than standard doors. You&rsquo;ll notice the difference in your garage&rsquo;s comfort, energy efficiency, and noise reduction.</p><p>The steel panels are treated with a multi-layer rust-prevention system, including galvanizing, a protective metal oxide layer, and a durable baked-on finish. The bottom of the door features a replaceable vinyl weather seal set in a rust-resistant aluminum retainer to keep out drafts, rain, and debris. Safety is built in, too, with a patented Safe-T-Bracket&reg; that helps prevent injuries during maintenance.</p><p>All Intellicore&reg; insulated doors come with smooth-gliding, 10-ball nylon rollers and extra-strong 14-gauge steel hinges for reliable, quiet operation. Removable window grilles make cleaning easy. Plus, every door complies with 2015 IECC air infiltration requirement of 0.40 cfm/ft2 or less (IECC, Section C402.5.2) to help keep your home more comfortable year-round.</p>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Canyon Ridge Modern","DisplayIndex":6,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/canyon-ridge-modern","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>*Black, white, bronze and charcoal only available in Mahogany.</p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Every Canyon Ridge&reg; Modern garage door comes standard with sleek Spade Lift Handles, designed for a clean look and easy operation. If you want to take your door&rsquo;s style a step further, you can upgrade to our optional Aluminum Grip Handle in various color options, which offers a more modern, streamlined feel and is available in a variety of finishes to match your home&rsquo;s aesthetic. </p>","DesignDisclaimer":"","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Modern Steel™","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/modern-steel-flush_fullview-window-black-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=db7014e9_14","Id":"170","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/modern-steel-collection","DisplayIndex":7,"ShortDescription":"Subtle modern beauty, simple up-keep","AlternativeText":"Modern Steel"},{"Title":"Avante<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> – Now Available with C-Power™ Technology","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/tnahcpower01showcase.webp?sfvrsn=e1a1ed6c_1","Id":"16","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/avante","DisplayIndex":9,"ShortDescription":"Aluminum and glass doors that make your garage a stunning focal point, providing natural light by day and a dramatic glow at night","AlternativeText":"Avante"},{"Title":"Reserve<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Wood Modern","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/reserve-modern-design-cladding-solid-garage-door-595.webp?sfvrsn=b04b7a7a_9","Id":"25","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/reserve-modern-contemporary-garage-doors","DisplayIndex":17,"ShortDescription":"Clean lines and simple forms invite the beauty of natural wood stand out","AlternativeText":"Reserve Wood Modern"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-canyonridgebr-20-1.webp?sfvrsn=9c9dfc36_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-CANYONRIDGEBR-20.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Installation Manual for Residential Sectional Insulated Steel Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-insulatedresi.webp?sfvrsn=15f3a601_3","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150077_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Canyon Ridge Care and Maintenance","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/care-and-maintenance/cmb-4150084_en.webp?sfvrsn=d710b9a2_2","Type":"Finish & Care","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CMB-4150084_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Handle Installation for Modern Series","ImageUrl":"https://www.cl